ound-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: 36pt;\">\r\n		<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt;\">\r\n			<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7f90318a-7fff-fa2f-0e72-fcbf83e74388\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Obligations Fondamentales :</span></b>\r\n		</h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt;\">\r\n	<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7f90318a-7fff-fa2f-0e72-fcbf83e74388\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Le Membre ou l&rsquo;Abonn&eacute; a, de mani&egrave;re g&eacute;n&eacute;rale, pour obligations fondamentales (ci-apr&egrave;s, les &quot;Obligations Fondamentales&quot;) de :</span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\">\r\n		<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n			<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-7f90318a-7fff-fa2f-0e72-fcbf83e74388\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Utiliser les Servi