(218,	1,	'2018-12-14 14:10:30',	'2018-12-14 13:10:30',	'<p>\r\n	<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n<!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}-->	</style>\r\n	The true story of life in Jersey during the German&nbsp;occupation. The hardship, the heartache and the&nbsp;heroism, in the words of the people who were&nbsp;there.Experience a real-life adventure game, with mysterious puzzles and brain-teasing clues! In our amazing Escape Rooms, you will have to find clues, break codes, solve puzzles and find the key to your freedom. Using your powers of observation and problem-solving, you and your team will have to work together to escape.<br />\r\n	La v&eacute;ritable histoire de la vie &agrave; Jersey pendant l&#39;occupation allemande. Les difficult&eacute;s, le chagrin et l&#39;h&eacute;ro&iuml;sme, au travers des mots et t&eacute;moignages des personnes pr&eacute;sentes. Exp&eacute;rimentez un jeu d&#39;aventure dans la vie r&eacute;elle, avec des &eacute;nigmes myst&eacute;rieuses et des indices d&eacute;concertants! Dans nos incroyables salles d&#39;&eacute;vasion, vous devrez trouver des indices, d&eacute;chiffrer des codes, r&eacute;soudre des &eacute;nigmes et trouver la cl&eacute; de votre libert&eacute;. En utilisant vos capacit&eacute;s d&#39;observation et de r&eacute;solution de probl&egrave;mes, vous et votre &eacute;quipe devrez travailler ensemble pour vous &eacute;chapper.\r\n</p>\r\n',	'Jersey War Tunnels',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'jersey-war-tunnels',	'',	'',	'2018-12-14 14:10:30',	'2018-12-14 13:10:30',	'',	0,	'http://localhost/wordpress/Cpartie/?post_type=pro&#038;p=218',	0,	'pro',	'',	0),
